me\">\n        《黑白大廚2》據指有過千名廚師參加選拔。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4059059/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"第4季度公開的《體能之巔：亞洲》找來菲律賓拳王帕奎奧（Manny Pacquiao）參賽。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/07411c523a91f92fd261723451eb7ad2/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-04_at_16_03_21.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        第4季度公開的《體能之巔：亞洲》找來菲律賓拳王帕奎奧（Manny Pacquiao）參賽。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4059064/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《體能之巔：亞洲》在第4季度公開。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28d2239932e0bd1abaa2f71ae6cd0c0c/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-04_at_16_02_30_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《體能之巔：亞洲》在第4季度公開。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>電影有金多美主演的《巨洪》</h2>\n<p>電影方面，有金多美主演的《巨洪》，任時完主演兼第3季度上映的《Mantis》，薛景求主演及第4季度上映的《Good News》；另外金泰梨及洪慶聲演的首部韓國動畫《Lost in Starlight》，柳俊烈主演的《Revelations》等都在今年推出。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
