            "title": "旺角小巴撞電動輪椅老婦受傷 熱心途人助急救",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"旺角小巴撞電動輪椅老婦受傷 熱心途人助急救。 FB：突發馬路車cam大全\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ed2713916ab2e11e78bc8017da6e32cb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020417124514886.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">旺角小巴撞電動輪椅老婦受傷 熱心途人助急救。 FB：突發馬路車cam大全</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角花園街及弼街交界，今日（2月4日）下午4時許，一部小巴與撞倒一名老婦。網上片段所見，老婦懷疑乘坐電動輪椅，於馬路行駛時與小巴相撞。事後大批熱心途人上前協助，將攙扶至路邊石壆休息，等候救援。事件中老婦受輕傷，經救護員治理後毋須送院，意外原因仍在調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4059245/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為旺角花園街及弼街交界。 FB：突發馬路車cam大全\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a434a11bed867dfea6b3b96c8b4bedc/2025-02/videoframe_6012.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為旺角花園街及弼街交界。 FB：突發馬路車cam大全\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
